Recommendations (if you need to act on this assessment)
- If you need to compare suppliers or partners: ask Microchip for (a) SBTi validation status or plans, (b) absolute annual Scope 1/2/3 tables for 2020–2024, (c) list of contracted renewables (PPAs/RECs) with MW/MWh and start dates, and (d) site‑level water/energy savings metrics for key fabs. These data points will materially change grading if supplied and verified.
- For procurement/engineering: evaluate Microchip’s mSiC and low‑power FPGA offerings for product energy budgets — these are tangible innovation levers to reduce downstream lifecycle emissions.

